description: Discover the epitome of luxury living in this stunning studio condo at the prestigious Echelon building in Boston's Seaport District. With its sleek modern design, this residence features an open-concept layout, floor-to-ceiling windows, and premium finishes that perfectly blend style and functionality. Residents of Echelon enjoy access to an array of world-class amenities, including three distinct pool experiences: an indoor pool, a resort-style outdoor pool, and a rooftop plunge pool with breathtaking views. Stay active in the state-of-the-art fitness center, offering cutting-edge equipment and fitness classes, or indulge in relaxation at the on-site spa complete with steam rooms and saunas. The Sky Lounge and rooftop terrace provide an ideal setting for taking in panoramic city and harbor views, while the resident library and wine room offer sophisticated spaces to unwind or entertain.
